---
title: Ultimate Kung Pao Style Prawns and Jasmine Rice with Tenderstem®, Spring Onion and Cashew Nuts
description: Looking for a taste of everyday luxury? This Ultimate Kung Pao Style Prawns and Jasmine Rice is our best ever version, with premium ingredients for an extra special twist on a classic recipe.
